Collaborative editor for Google Drive.
Create new public websites right from the Google Drive "Create" menu.
Copy one of the provided examples to get started with your favorite framework.

* Realtime collaboration
* Comments and Replies
* Revision History
* Edit single files
* Create a workspace to edit multiple project files at once
* Publish to Google Cloud
* Custom domains
